Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:02.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers who\Nkeep a close eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:42.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on the countless souls,\Ngood and evil, that fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:48.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen, who has brought chaos\Nupon the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has begun to set his plan into motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:54.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancars, created by Aizen\Nusing the Hogyoku,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.52,0:01:58.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a material that removes the boundaries\Nbetween Soul Reapers and Hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,appear in Karakura Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:03.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto? Are they like us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:05.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Hirako and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:10.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and his friends emerge as\Nvictors in a tough battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,against Ulquiorra and Yammy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but sustain injuries that are\Nmore serious than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo also becomes fearful
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:21.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the existence of the Hollow within him\Nand loses his will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is at that time that Hitsugaya\Nand several other Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.84,0:02:28.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are dispatched from Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:31.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're afraid of losing,\Njust become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're afraid of the Hollow\Nwithin you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,then become stronger until\Nyou're able to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the kind of man\Nyou are in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:46.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia manages to talk sense\Ninto the depressed Ichigo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and restore his confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, at that time,\NGrimmjow, an Arrancar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:58.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who was displeased with how\NUlquiorra handled his fight with Ichigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.60,0:03:02.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,comes to the World of the Living\Nwith several other Arrancars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You will show them no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If they show even a glimmer\Nof Spiritual Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:21.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:25.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:27.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:28.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:30.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,1...2...3...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:31.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Six of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:33.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they headed here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're searching for\NSpiritual Pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're not coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.60,0:03:42.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not interested in the size\Nof the Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They just want to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They intend to kill every human who\Nhas even a little Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:53.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida should have zero Spiritual Pressure\Nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Chad and Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As for Inoue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:03.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hitsugaya and\NLieutenant Matsumoto are nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be safer than other places!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:11.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's...one approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're here, huh? This way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yumichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:33.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Run to a place where\Nyou won't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:35.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Orihime Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having the gigai watch her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:44.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that she does not participate\Nin the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:45.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready, Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:48.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:11.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:20.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:29.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancar Undécimo,\NI am called Shawlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:33.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain of Squad 10,\NToshiro Hitsugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:45.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 10 Captain...\NMy, my, how impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:51.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...I aimed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:51.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:53.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:56.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,missed big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do that, Chad!\NYour treatment's not over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back and make Inoue well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's a miss or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:53.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is decided after you fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:57.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:02.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thrash the whole lot of you,\Nthen I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That each one of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,missed big time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:18.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I would be dead...\Nif Ichigo had come a second later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I would definitely be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- My injury is-\N- Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:35.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind... Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:46.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...all right. I'll leave it to you, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay, Sado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:02.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need me to watch\Nyour back anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:08.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I no longer able to fight\Nside-by-side with you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:19.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now... How shall I go\Nabout thrashing you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I saw Sado on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:32.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:37.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing... Just to stay back\Nand let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, stay back and let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:57.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.16,0:09:02.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're like that before the battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you risk losing your life senselessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:12.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia...you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:18.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Soul Reaper powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:28.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Soul Reaper powers did not return\Nbecause of Urahara's gigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So by removing the gigai and\Nliving in Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,which overflows with reishi,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it was only a matter of time before\NI regained my spirit power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:42.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Overflows with reishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:46.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts absorbed the reishi\Nin Soul Society and gained power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't as rapid as those guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Soul Reapers also reap\Nthe same benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:03.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your powers hadn't returned\Nduring the battle with the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:07.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After Captain Aizen's rebellion,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to recuperate and\Nrestore my spirit power slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But those plans went awry
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,due to the sudden appearance\Nof the Bounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:19.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Society was in total confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:23.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it was an emergency situation\Nwith no one in Central 46.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the midst of all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:29.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bounts appeared in Karakura Town\Nand you all stood on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seireitei had no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:36.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but to use someone\Nwho was familiar with the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:43.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone familiar with the town\Nand the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:48.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's you, Hanataro,\NGanju and Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think there was a problem\Nwith the personnel selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You all were pretty useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:10:58.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be good and stay back! Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:02.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Pyon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:07.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Female Soul Reaper Association's\Nmost popular Soul Candy, "Chappy."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:10.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the first Soul Candy I tried to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:14.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mix-up and instead,\NI got Kon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:18.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she's the one who\Nwas supposed to enter my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate to admit it,\Nbut I'm happy it was Kon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:23.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:24.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- But damn, you're strong!\N- Rude! You're rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Actually, I'm shocked too.\N- Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:31.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Before you returned here,\N- Oww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue treated my wound\Nand after that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:35.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my spirit power was restored to\Nan unbelievable degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- And...\N- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:41.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:55.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrancar Dieciseis, D Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:58.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 13-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no need to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:04.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I listened to the names of\Neveryone I'm about to thrash,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,there wouldn't be enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:16.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At least remember the name\Nof my zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Somenomai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:34.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:41.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What...is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad, Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My true battlefield is in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:01.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sword,\Nwhich freezes the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has no effect in an aerial battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki is not a sword\Nthat "freezes the ground."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything within this circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is the freezing domain of\Nmy Sodenoshirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:37.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:40.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! If you're not quiet,\NI shall silence you with force! Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:42.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that pyon, pyon crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts so bad, I can't keep quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:46.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:46.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna break my arm!\NYou're gonna break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:51.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pummel you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to get pummeled,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll kill you before\Nyou kill me! Pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:14:00.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your job is to just hold me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:03.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Yay!\NI'll just make your arm go pyon♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:09.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Huh?\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:13.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you…okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that one?!\NDid you beat it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I wouldn’t have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:27.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:32.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sodenoshirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:37.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia’s ice-snow type zanpakuto\Nhas been declared
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the most beautiful in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:47.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The blade, the guard, the hilt…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a zanpakuto like pure snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:51.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it’s all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:53.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:57.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the present time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia has the strength of\Na seated officer! Pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if she is assigned a seat,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the risk level of her missions\Nwill be much greater
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,than if she were to remain\Nin the rank-and-file.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:14.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, a certain person did not want\Nto put Rukia in the face of danger,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,approached the captains and\Nrequested that she be taken off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the list of candidates\Nto be assigned seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain person…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:23.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, pyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:34.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I said it’s all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:37.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So just get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just make your arm go pyon♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you\Ngoing to keep that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already,\Nwe must hurry and…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Was D Roy killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll just have to…\Nkill the two of you together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do, Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:16.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m Arrancar Seis, Grimmjow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So D Roy has been beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That scum…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He begged to come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:36.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I brought him,\Nand this is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where’re you looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:43.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.12,0:16:50.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Lord Aizen took him\Nunder his wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:53.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,scum is scum, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever fought D Roy was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:04.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That D Roy was unbelievably useless\Nas an Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:11.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have no luck at all!\NYou’re up against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll be tossed around…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and you’ll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:21.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s happening?\NThis is so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it’s not nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes… All this racket\Nin the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these delinquents anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:46.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Mizuho…\Nbuy your own juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:51.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man, I hate this area.\NIt’s so dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:55.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve been seeing ghostly figures\Na lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:59.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. I don’t believe in them.\NI don’t, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They still give me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:06.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:13.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the guy\Nwho’s always battling beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,'Evening, Mr.Af!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:20.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Filming again tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\NMr. Af stands for Mr. Afro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:27.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Shut up!\NI have no time for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you cherish your life,\Ndon’t hang around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All the lives in the world\Nwon’t be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:39.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s with him?\NI was just trying to say hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.04,0:18:42.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He could’ve at least stopped\Nfor a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen the TV show\Nthat he's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it’s on a cable channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What’s this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:08.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What is this?!\NWhat’s happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:18.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Agh! Y-You’re the one I saw\Nin school this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing\Nin the middle of the night
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,carrying a Japanese sword…\Ncovered in blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:24.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re the one from this afternoon…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:38.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter?\NIs that all a Soul Reaper is?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Soul Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:44.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reaper?\NAs in real Soul Reapers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these people talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.16,0:19:55.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a juicy proposition…\NYou’re interested, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:57.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…err…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on the proposition,\Ndon’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, we don’t have a room\Nfor the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:06.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:09.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re now involved in this fight\Nand about to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:13.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Err…I think you’re the one\Nwho’s about to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:18.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save you from that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:22.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So put us up at your house\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:23.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not “huh”!\NIs it gonna be “yes” or “no”?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:35.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:37.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven’t told me\Nyour name yet, you big oaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:47.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?\NI’m Arrancar Trece…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:57.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Introductions aren’t necessary\Nsince I’m about to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:00.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you and I have\Ndifferent styles of protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:11.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,“Always introduce yourself to\Nthe one you’re about to kill.”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:17.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the final etiquette that\NI teach to every pupil I train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:20.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you’re putting your life\Non the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:26.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you’d want to know who\Nit was that killed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.76,0:21:33.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Know me as Third Seat of\NZaraki’s Squad, Ikkaku Madarame!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But don’t bother to tell me\Nyour name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:39.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure\Nyou remember my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the name of the man…\NWho will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:13.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:18.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,…And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.55,0:23:23.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, the hard skin of\Nan Arrancar is written as “steel skin”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:25.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and is read “Hierro.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.24,0:23:27.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumoto, I wonder which\Nis thicker…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Theirs or the skin on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh please! Don’t compare\Nmy soft womanly complexion to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:34.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think yours looks firmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:37.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So on and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s about it in\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:43.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… \NContinue, but increase observations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:46.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! And this…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:48.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:24:00.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lady Yoruichi. So gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:05.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Her daily attire is splendid too!